data.description: Welcome Home! This is a hidden gem, tucked away off the main road providing lots of privacy.  This more than half acre lot has room to build a huge shop, a pool or what your heart desires.  A garden has been cultivated for years in the back corner.  Plenty of room for parking all the toys.  The exterior of the home received a facelift 3 years ago with all new stucco.  New furnace in 2020, new water heater in 2021.  City sewer for convenience but well water saving you $$.  The balcony off the master overlooking the property allows for sunrise & sunset views in the south facing back yard.  So many possibilities.
